OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784663290
OL,3,CTrump imposes 50% tariffs on Canadian
OL,4,Cgoods including cars, alcohol and
OL,5,Ccheese
OL,7,FPresident Trump has announced 50%
OL,8,Ftariffs on the majority of Canadian
OL,9,Fgoods, in retaliation for what he
OL,10,Fclaims is unfair discrimination by
OL,11,FCanada against American alcohol, dairy
OL,12,Fproducts and cars.
OL,14,FThe sweeping tariffs will come into
OL,15,Feffect in 30 days, but exclude key
OL,16,Fexports like energy products, potash
OL,17,Fwhich is used to make fertiliser, fish
OL,18,Fand critical minerals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
