PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784663290
OL,3,CTrump imposes 50% tariffs on Canadian
OL,4,Cgoods including cars, alcohol and
OL,5,Ccheese
OL,7,FThe Trump administration said Canada
OL,8,Fmust be held accountable for being one
OL,9,Fof the only countries other than China
OL,10,Fto have hit back at Trump's previous
OL,11,Ftariffs.
OL,13,FResponding to the tariffs, Canadian
OL,14,FPrime Minister Mark Carney said: "This
OL,15,Fis the latest in a series of
OL,16,Funilateral US trade actions that began
OL,17,Fwith the US imposing a series of
OL,18,Ftariffs in direct violation of the
OL,19,FCanada United States Mexico Agreement
OL,20,F(CUSMA)."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784663290
OL,3,CTrump imposes 50% tariffs on Canadian
OL,4,Cgoods including cars, alcohol and
OL,5,Ccheese
OL,7,FHe said Canada "believes in the
OL,8,Fbenefits of free and fair trade" and
OL,9,Fis "ready to engage intensively to
OL,10,Faddress outstanding issues with the
OL,11,FUS."
OL,13,FPremier of Ontario Doug Ford said
OL,14,FCanada should retaliate with their own
OL,15,Ftariffs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
