PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784663290
OL,3,CTrump imposes 50% tariffs on Canadian
OL,4,Cgoods including cars, alcohol and
OL,5,Ccheese
OL,7,FThough not officially stated as the
OL,8,Freason behind the tariffs, President
OL,9,FTrump's announcement comes in the wake
OL,10,Fof his threat to penalise Canada for
OL,11,Fwildfire smoke which blew across the
OL,12,Fborder damaging air quality in the USA.
OL,14,FThe Trump administration's latest move
OL,15,Fwill further damage the economic
OL,16,Frelationship between the neighbouring
OL,17,Fcountries, and could increase the risk
OL,18,Fof soaring inflation in America.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
