OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784663290
OL,3,CTrump imposes 50% tariffs on Canadian
OL,4,Cgoods including cars, alcohol and
OL,5,Ccheese
OL,7,FIn response to previous tariffs, The
OL,8,FWhite House said all but two Canadian
OL,9,Fprovinces and territories retaliated
OL,10,Fby stopping purchasing and selling
OL,11,FAmerican alcohol.
OL,13,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FTariffs are taxes imposed by
OL,19,Fgovernments on goods and services
OL,20,Fbeing imported by another country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
