PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784663290
OL,3,CTrump imposes 50% tariffs on Canadian
OL,4,Cgoods including cars, alcohol and
OL,5,Ccheese
OL,7,FThe new tariffs will affect goods
OL,8,Fpreviously protected from import taxes
OL,9,Funder the 2020 United States-Mexico-
OL,10,FCanada Agreement (USMCA), an agreement
OL,11,Fwhich was not renewed by the US.
OL,13,FThe move could threaten a trade war
OL,14,Fbetween the US and Canada and increase
OL,15,Finflation when Trump previously
OL,16,Fpromised to lower prices for Americans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
