PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1784663290
OL,3,CTrump imposes 50% tariffs on Canadian
OL,4,Cgoods including cars, alcohol and
OL,5,Ccheese
OL,7,FIn April last year his "Liberation
OL,8,FDay" tariffs caused a market meltdown
OL,9,Fwith the threat of higher inflation
OL,10,Fand recession, prompting Trump to cut
OL,11,Fback the rates and negotiate tariffs.
OL,13,FIn February the Supreme Court ruled
OL,14,Fthat Trump lacked the legal authority
OL,15,Fto impose the tariffs and made the
OL,16,Fgovernment refund the money to
OL,17,Faffected companies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
